text: I'm sorry for keeping you waiting!

Oh, it's nothing.
no worries at all.

Um, may I get something to drink?
I ran all the way here, and I'm really thirsty…

I probably won't have it, but if that person
brings a mixed drink, I might be put off.

No, that won't happen.
I mean, come on…
Sorry for keeping you waiting again!

Man, this is so good!
It's a mix of melon soda and grape juice!
